.TH "LIGHTNING-SCB" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-scb \- Static Channel Backup emit + restore
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning scb
[\fIsubcommand\fR] [\fIargs\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.nf
lightning scb — Static Channel Backup emit + restore.

Implements FEAT-185 §SCB. clightning calls these
`staticbackup` (emit) and `emergencyrecover` (restore).

Subcommands:
  emit [--out <file>]     write an SCB blob. Default location:
                          <active-wallet>/scb-<utc>.bin
  restore <file>          initiate SCB recovery (force-closes)
.fi
.SH USAGE
.nf
usage: lightning scb emit [--out <file>]
       lightning scb restore <file>
.fi
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.BR lightning (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Part of the \fBlightning\fR educational Lightning Network frontend.
